<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧ - <span class="c2">(٣٠٢٣)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى،</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>. <span class="c2">(ح)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>، أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6555">النَّضْرُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَا جَمِيعًا:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ فِي حَدِيثِ ابْنِ جَعْفَرٍ: <span class="c2">« نَزَلَتْ فِي آخِرِ مَا أُنْزِلَ»</span>.<span class="c5"> وَفِي حَدِيثِ النَّضْرِ:</span> إِنَّهَا لَمِنْ آخِرِ مَا أُنْزِلَتْ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>